        <sponsor name-id="S197">Mr. McCain</sponsor> (for himself and <cosponsor name-id="S317">Mr. Barrasso</cosponsor>) introduced the following bill; which was read twice and referred to the <committee-name committee-id="SSFI00">Committee on Finance</committee-name>
      </action-desc>
